OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,FStephen McCullagh has been found
OL,6,Fguilty of the murder of Natalie
OL,7,FMcNally on December 18 2022 at her
OL,8,Fhome in Lurgan.
OL,10,FTimeline of key events:
OL,12,FAugust 7 2022: Stephen McCullagh sends
OL,13,Fhis first WhatsApp message to Natalie
OL,14,FMcNally after they made contact on the
OL,15,Fonline dating app Bumble. His first
OL,16,Fmessage read: "Hey Nat, it's that
OL,17,Frobot weirdo from Bumble" and they
OL,18,Fdiscussed meeting for their first date
OL,19,Fthat week.
OL,26,@xD@OOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/16
