FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,FOver the next 133 days the two were to
OL,6,Fexchange hundreds of messages. The
OL,7,Fprosecution in McCullagh's murder
OL,8,Ftrial said that he had also accessed
OL,9,FMs McNally's phone and saw messages
OL,10,Fshe had exchanged with other men.
OL,12,FOctober: McCullagh meets Ms McNally's
OL,13,Ffamily for the first time.
OL,15,FNovember: The McNally family are told
OL,16,Fthat the couple are expecting a baby.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
