PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,FDecember 14/15: McCullagh pre-records
OL,6,FThe Violent Night Christmas Live
OL,7,FGaming Stream. The six hour and four
OL,8,Fminute gaming session shows McCullagh
OL,9,Fplaying Grand Theft Auto while
OL,10,Fdrinking alcohol, swearing and at one
OL,11,Fpoint repeatedly shouting at a
OL,12,Fcharacter in the game to die. During
OL,13,Fthe session McCullagh makes repeated
OL,14,Fmention that it is being broadcast
OL,15,Flive on the Sunday (December 18).
OL,17,FDecember 16/17: McCullagh tells
OL,18,Ffriends he will broadcast a gaming
OL,19,Fsession live on Sunday evening.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
