PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,FDecember 18: Ms McNally is in
OL,6,FMcCullagh's home in Woodland Gardens
OL,7,Fin Lisburn while he is searching
OL,8,Ftimetables for a bus from Dunmurry to
OL,9,FLurgan and a later train from Lurgan
OL,10,Fback to Lisburn. Ms McNally later
OL,11,Fleaves McCullagh's house to go to her
OL,12,Fparents' home to watch the World Cup
OL,13,Ffinal between Argentina and France
OL,14,Fbefore returning to her own house at
OL,15,FSilverwood Green in Lurgan.
OL,17,F4pm: McCullagh posts an advert on
OL,18,FYoutube about his "live" gaming
OL,19,Fsession.
OL,26,@zD@SOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
