PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,F5.57pm: McCullagh messages Ms McNally
OL,6,Fsaying that he is "off to stream the
OL,7,Fnight away". She replies: "Good luck,
OL,8,FI might have a peek at your livestream
OL,9,Flater."
OL,11,F6pm: The pre-recorded livestream
OL,12,Fbegins. McCullagh's telephone becomes
OL,13,Finactive.
OL,15,F6.36pm: A man is captured on CCTV
OL,16,Fwalking with a bag close to
OL,17,FMcCullagh's house. The prosecution in
OL,18,Fthe trial said the man was McCullagh.
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@KO]oD@[OUqD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/16
