PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,F7.36pm: Bus CCTV shows the man with
OL,6,Fhis face covered travelling from
OL,7,FDunmurry to Lurgan. After getting off
OL,8,Fthe bus in Lurgan, he is tracked on a
OL,9,Fnumber of cameras travelling down
OL,10,FMarket Street towards William Street,
OL,11,FLough Road and into Silverwood Green,
OL,12,Fwhere Ms McNally lives.
OL,14,F8.24pm: Ms McNally logs in to YouTube
OL,15,Fto watch part of McCullagh's
OL,16,Flivestream gaming session.
OL,18,F8.51pm: McCullagh enters Ms McNally's
OL,19,Fhouse.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
