CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,F9.31pm: McCullagh leaves Ms McNally's
OL,6,Fhouse.
OL,8,F9.49pm: A man is seen on CCTV getting
OL,9,Finto a taxi near Fa Joe's bar in
OL,10,FLurgan.
OL,12,F11.12pm: The taxi arrives at
OL,13,FMcCullagh's house at Woodlands in
OL,14,FLisburn. He is seen on CCTV throwing
OL,15,Ftwo items over a hedge.
OL,17,F11.16pm: McCullagh's phone is unlocked
OL,18,Fand becomes active.
OL,20,FDecember 19:
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
