PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,F12.05am: The recording of the gaming
OL,6,Fbroadcast is manually stopped.
OL,8,F12:08am: McCullagh messages Ms McNally.
OL,10,F5.05pm: McCullagh messages Ms McNally
OL,11,F"Are you ok?".
OL,13,F5.25pm: He messages "Getting a little
OL,14,Fworried, let me know you are safe".
OL,16,F6.55pm: McCullagh orders a KFC.
OL,18,F9.07pm: He messages Ms McNally stating
OL,19,Fhe is "very concerned now".
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@MO]uD@UOUvD@bO]{D@GOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
