FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,F9.59pm: McCullagh arrives at Ms
OL,6,FMcNally's house in Lurgan and makes a
OL,7,F10-minute 999 call. He tells emergency
OL,8,Fservices "Please come as soon as you
OL,9,Fcan, she's pregnant, she's cold". He
OL,10,Fis asked by the call handler: "Is the
OL,11,Fpatient breathing?" and responds
OL,12,Ftearfully "No, she's gone", adding
OL,13,F"there's blood everywhere". He tells
OL,14,Fthe call handler Ms McNally was 15
OL,15,Fweeks' pregnant.
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@`O]rD@_OUsD@SO]tD@KOUtD@ZO]uD@
OL,26,AAOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
