CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,FDecember 25: McCullagh attends a wake
OL,6,Ffor Ms McNally at her parents' home on
OL,7,FChristmas Day.
OL,9,FJanuary 26 2023: McCullagh visits the
OL,10,FMcNally family home again. When he
OL,11,Fdeparts the house, he leaves his phone
OL,12,Fbehind and makes a 39-minute recording
OL,13,Fof the family speaking. He returns
OL,14,Flater to retrieve the phone.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
