PN,44413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,FJanuary 28: More than 1,000 people
OL,6,Fattend a rally in Lurgan in memory of
OL,7,FMs McNally. McCullagh attends the
OL,8,Fevent. A video montage of images of Ms
OL,9,FMcNally is played and the crowd are
OL,10,Ftold it was put together by McCullagh,
OL,11,F"Natalie's loving partner".
OL,13,FJanuary 31: McCullagh is arrested
OL,14,Fagain by police.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
