PN,44414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,FFebruary 1: During police interview
OL,6,FMcCullagh replies "no comment" to a
OL,7,Fseries of questions about Ms McNally's
OL,8,Fmurder. He is confronted for the first
OL,9,Ftime with evidence that his gaming
OL,10,Fsession had been pre-recorded. A
OL,11,Fdetective tells him that his devices
OL,12,Fhad been examined and there was no
OL,13,Fuser generated activity during the
OL,14,Fhours when he claimed to be
OL,15,Fbroadcasting live. He answers: "That
OL,16,Fis literally impossible because you
OL,17,Fcan see it on YouTube."
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@^O]wD@`OUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
