PN,44415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774296676
OL,3,CFrom dating app to cold-blooded murder
OL,5,FFollowing the interview McCullagh
OL,6,Fprovides a statement to police in
OL,7,Fwhich he says the gaming session had
OL,8,Fbeen pre-recorded in advance.
OL,10,FHe added: "I think it is obvious the
OL,11,Ftrue killer of Natalie has left a
OL,12,Fclear circumstantial trail to link me
OL,13,Fto the murder."
OL,15,FFebruary 2: Stephen McCullagh is
OL,16,Fcharged with the murder of Natalie
OL,17,FMcNally.
OL,19,FFebruary 23 2026: McCullagh goes on
OL,20,Ftrial for the murder of Natalie
OL,21,FMcNally at Belfast Crown Court.
OL,26,@rD@KOUuD@OO]
